There is some bug in TPB when copying file name. I copy and paste the full name "2013 Motocross GP of Trentino..." but it leaves out a few letters. 

Hope the tags help you find the file.

Don't worry! The name is not important!
Thank you.

Thank you once again, so appreciated from Canada.  I agree with agm137, just as long as we can find it, doesn't really matter what it's called.  I search under mxgp and if not there I'll try "of Italy" or whatever country is next on the schedule.  If you keep putting them on, we'll find them.   You da man!!
